317
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,670
Just a touch, and he can make Su Yishui

318
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,470
fall victim to it

319
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:33,390
without even realizing it.

320
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:34,750
In that case,

321
00:12:34,970 --> 00:12:35,970
he'll be no match for you, My Lord,

322
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,080
and will be at your mercy.

323
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:38,630
Well done.

324
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,360
What about the other fruit?

325
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,790
Bai Baishan doesn't know,

326
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:44,090
but he said

327
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:46,120
Su Yishui values his Junior Xue the most.

328
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,150
And that girl always has a branch

329
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:50,030
