333
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,390
You're the little disciple

334
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,960
Su Yishui values the most?

335
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,240
What's your name?

336
00:13:10,030 --> 00:13:11,270
My master says, when we are out,

337
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,120
we shouldn't

338
00:13:12,150 --> 00:13:13,360
tell strangers our names.

339
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,360
Sir, I dare not

340
00:13:14,390 --> 00:13:15,320
disobey my master's order.

341
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,150
He's got sharp ears

342
00:13:17,780 --> 00:13:18,940
and can hear us

343
00:13:19,190 --> 00:13:20,830
even from outside.

344
00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:33,600
Where is your master?

345
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,540
He's been waiting outside.

346
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,240
He asked me to invite you, Immortal Master Wei,

347
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,000
out to meet him.

348
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,380
My master said

349
00:13:39,530 --> 00:13:40,490
if there's anything you want to know,

350
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:41,670
you can ask him directly.

351
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:43,030
Don't bother going to such lengths.

352
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,080
Go check it out.

353
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:46,600
Got it.

354
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:50,080
My Lord!

355
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:52,440
Go after her! Now!

356
00:13:52,900 --> 00:13:54,090
But Su Yishui is also here.

357
00:13:54,490 --> 00:13:55,170
You're even dumber

358
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,200
