362
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:00,270
Go and get her!

363
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:01,950
She might be the other fruit.

364
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:03,750
Yes, My Lord.

365
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:12,550
Wei Jiu is here.

366
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:13,880
We can't touch Senior Bai for now.

367
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:14,320
Let's run.

368
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:14,970
Okay.

369
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:46,480
Let's go!

370
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:48,360
Ranran.

371
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:49,750
Junior Xue,

372
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:50,670
