373
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:53,550
We can't...

374
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:07,200
My whip loves blood the most.

375
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,440
Once it smells the scent of blood,

376
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,130
I just can't hold it back.

377
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:13,840
Move!

378
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,060
Use the Exorcising Formation!

379
00:15:21,090 --> 00:15:21,540
Okay!

380
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,150
Just a fragile formation.

381
00:15:38,310 --> 00:15:38,960
One wisp of qi...

382
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:43,270
It's her!

383
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:49,560
To break the galaxy!

384
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,020
Mu Qingge...

385
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,240
I won't let you steal my power again!

386
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:06,150
Thought you really had something up your sleeve.

387
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:08,770
Go to hell!

388
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:11,840
Ranran!

389
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,670
Master...

390
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:26,240
Senior Bai is in the courtyard of Huaihua Lane.

391
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,910
Wei Jiu has poisoned him

392
00:16:27,910 --> 00:16:28,510
to harm you.

393
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:29,930
You must be careful.

394
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:30,400
Silence.

395
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:32,010
Let me help you recover and ease the pain.

396
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,920
How dare you hurt my disciple?

397
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:29,510
Retreat!

398
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:30,720
You ask for it...

399
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:13,240
Xue Ranran is Mu Qingge?

400
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:15,070
Su Yishui,

401
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,720
you've been fooling me all along.

402
00:18:19,630 --> 00:18:20,280
Both of you

403
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,200
deserve to die.

404
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:38,510
Feng!

405
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:39,720
Feng!

406
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:42,880
Your Highness.

407
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:48,310
That beast is running wild again?

408
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,320
You go back to the palace now

409
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,490
to keep an eye on it.

410
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,620
Once we restore the Four-Way Waterways,

411
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,110
everything will be fine.

412
00:18:59,350 --> 00:18:59,830
Yes, Your Highness.

413
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,200
Your Highness,

414
00:19:09,720 --> 00:19:11,110
among the squads sent to investigate the waterways,

415
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:12,690
only those heading to the Puxin Village

416
00:19:12,720 --> 00:19:13,680
have not returned yet.

417
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:15,000
There's no news from them either.

418
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,830
No collapses in other areas.

419
00:19:19,790 --> 00:19:21,550
Then the Puxin Village must have undergone a collapse,

420
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:23,240
blocking the waterway.

421
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,240
Can't wait any longer.

422
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:26,810
Tell everyone to gear up

423
00:19:27,270 --> 00:19:28,350
and set off for the Puxin Village right away.

424
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:29,110
Understood!

425
00:19:36,070 --> 00:19:37,110
Why are you not after her?

426
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,790
It's my fault, Your Highness.

427
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,160
I followed Master Mu

428
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,340
and saw her secretly meet Scarlet Sect's Wei Jiu.

429
00:19:41,910 --> 00:19:43,060
Then I just lost track of Master Mu.

430
00:19:45,030 --> 00:19:46,680
Qingge hates people like Wei Jiu.

431
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:48,160
How could she meet him in secret?

432
00:19:51,720 --> 00:19:52,240
Something's off.

433
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:54,790
No matter how much people change,

434
00:19:56,030 --> 00:19:57,060
their true nature hardly alters.

435
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,680
Qingge has always been upfront.

436
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:01,440
Her ditching you

437
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,720
is already the biggest red flag.

438
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:09,000
She can't be Qingge.

439
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:19,960
Ranran...

440
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:26,720
Holy moly,

441
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,680
you're finally awake.

442
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:28,750
You've been

443
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:30,060
asleep for four days, you know?

444
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:31,400
Everything's in chaos out there.

445
00:20:32,470 --> 00:20:33,030
What?

446
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:35,000
I thought with Master here,

447
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:35,950
everything must be fine then.

448
00:20:36,310 --> 00:20:36,830
Could it be

449
00:20:37,160 --> 00:20:38,640
that Wei Jiu really injured Master?

450
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:39,650
Then Master...

451
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,310
That's not the case.

452
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:41,390
Calm down.

453
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:42,280
Don't let your wounds

454
00:20:42,310 --> 00:20:42,880
split open.

455
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:45,440
You should have seen it.

456
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:46,960
Master was terrifying that day.

457
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:48,750
He went on a killing spree all the way.

458
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:50,070
Those Scarlets

459
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:51,680
were burned to ashes right before us.

460
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:53,070
Not even a trace was left.

461
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,000
Master held you like this

462
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:56,310
and said,

463
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,000
"How dare you hurt my disciple?

464
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,310
You ask for it."

465
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:01,480
He held me?

466
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:05,000
Did he hold me all the way and bring me back?

467
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,680
What are you secretly thinking about?

468
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,680
Oh, God. You look so lost

469
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,440
in love.

470
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,550
But don't get in too deep

471
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:15,200
How can I control it?

472
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:16,920
Master is so nice.

473
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:19,790
Senior Bai won't agree with you.

474
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,030
Senior Bai is about to be expelled

475
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,350
from the sect by Master, you know?

476
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,920
The Horned Ghost Poison in you has been removed,

477
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,440
but it's diminished

478
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,440
your cultivation

479
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:29,680
in an irreversible way.

480
00:21:30,550 --> 00:21:31,640
Our master-disciple tie ends here.

481
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:33,160
You may leave now.

482
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:34,240
Master...

483
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,040
I-I didn't mean to do it.

484
00:21:37,450 --> 00:21:38,560
I've always looked up to you, Master.

485
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,960
I would never dare to betray you.

486
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:41,960
Master,

487
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,310
I-I don't want to be a good-for-nothing.

488
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,720
As omnipotent as you are,

489
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:47,240
you must have some way to help me.

490
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:48,480
Your Bai family

491
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,030
once saved a veteran Wester.

492
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:51,680
Out of gratitude for this favor,

493
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:52,590
I took you as my disciple.

494
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,550
But this time, you were blinded by lust,

495
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,110
causing your fellows to face danger and get hurt.

496
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:57,550
You should've paid for your sins with your life.

497
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,790
Expelling you from the sect

498
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:00,550
is me showing mercy.

499
00:22:01,510 --> 00:22:02,320
I've said all I need to say.

500
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,070
That's enough.

501
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:05,310
Master...

502
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:06,070
Master!

503
00:22:06,510 --> 00:22:07,200
Master!

504
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,880
Is it that serious?

505
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:21,510
Both Senior Gao and I were reluctant to see that happen.

506
00:22:21,590 --> 00:22:22,920
We wanted to plead with Master.

507
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,940
But Master only called Mr. Yu Chen

508
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:26,040
and Mr. Zeng Yi here

509
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:26,750
to take care of you.

510
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:28,480
Then he just went into seclusion, not seeing anyone.

511
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:31,160
Why did Master suddenly go into seclusion?

512
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,920
Su Yishui, look at yourself.

513
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,720
Given the way you lost control with rage,

514
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,640
you just don't look like a sovereign.

515
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,640
Aren't you afraid of frightening Ranran?

516
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:48,920
If I didn't already know the Spirit Spring

517
00:22:48,920 --> 00:22:49,550
had been taken away,

518
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:51,350
I would've thought you were repeating the same mistake.

519
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:03,720
What's going on?

520
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,850
Why can't I suppress this bloodlust?

521
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,160
Only the Demon's child

522
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:19,500
can summon it.

523
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:20,550
And you

524
00:23:21,370 --> 00:23:22,850
are the perfect, one-in-a-million

525
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,000
choice for the Demon's child.

526
00:23:24,790 --> 00:23:25,920
I have put this Spirit Spring

527
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:26,880
into your heart

528
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:30,200
and sacrificed your body to the Spirit Spring.

529
00:23:36,110 --> 00:23:36,680
I thought

530
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:38,890
it had all ended 19 years ago.

531
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,550
Could it be that...

532
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,400
The drop of Spirit Spring hasn't

533
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:43,200
been removed from my heart?

534
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:44,760
I got close to the Spirit Spring,

535
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:45,720
so it was triggered again?

536
00:24:14,200 --> 00:24:15,070
Couldn't find it.

537
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:17,400
Maybe it has hidden itself?

538
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:25,920
Master,

539
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:28,000
you've been in seclusion for days.

540
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:29,680
Did you get injured?

541
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:46,360
The Ice Lotus Technique can suppress the Spirit Spring.

542
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:47,200
It's hard to detect it.

543
00:24:48,310 --> 00:24:49,400
Once I find the Spirit Spring,

544
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,480
the drop in my heart, if still there,

545
00:24:51,750 --> 00:24:52,480
will surely respond.

546
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:54,200
I will finally have an answer.

547
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:13,830
Master?

548
00:25:17,890 --> 00:25:18,320
Master...

549
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:18,920
Don't move.

550
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,960
You haven't fully recovered. Why are you running around?

551
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:41,440
A Demon's child will always be a Demon's child.

552
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:44,750
He truly believes his fate has been changed?

553
00:25:45,550 --> 00:25:46,240
He's getting

554
00:25:46,270 --> 00:25:47,680
closer and closer to the Spirit Spring.

555
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,870
Once he finds the Spirit Spring,

556
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:52,000
it will repossess his body.

557
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:52,920
And we

558
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:56,260
will once again own the Demon's child.

559
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,590
Thank you, guardian.

560
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,790
The guardians have been

561
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,030
healing you for the past few days.

562
00:26:11,550 --> 00:26:12,880
But why hasn't it worked?

563
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:14,240
With my damaged Spirit Root,

564
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:16,350
It'll take me some more time to heal completely.

565
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:17,830
Tu Jiuyuan.

566
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:20,510
My Lord.

567
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:23,400
You may leave now.

568
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:24,000
Yes, My Lord.

569
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,200
Are you dead yet?

570
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:35,070
My Lord.

571
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:37,400
How useless you are.

572
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,310
You couldn't even catch

573
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,070
a little girl.

574
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,310
And you got yourself injured like this.

575
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,240
